reviewText: This is one of the most beautiful films I've ever seen. Only22 minutes long, it is beautifully enacted and filmed and directed by Bob Talbot who did the cinematography for Free Willy. The deep free diving sequences were done by a champion in the field. Amazing how they packed such a perfectly written and photographed film into just 22 minutes. It's a little movie with a big movie attitude you can watch again and again!!!
